data.description: Welcome to this exceptional, newly constructed home that is move-in ready. With 4 BRs & 3.5 Baths, this home features a spacious open floor plan to include a large dining area, formal living area, a chef’s kitchen equipped with state-of-the-art appliances, gas range, 42” cabinets, granite countertops, and center island, that seamlessly flows into a bright and inviting great room. The upstairs encompasses a large Primary BR with an Ensuite and an adjacent sitting room. A second floor balcony where you can sit and enjoy the serene views in a private setting. Additional amenities include a second-floor laundry room, 2 2-car garage, a tankless HW heater, and newly installed black wrought iron fencing. Also, take advantage of low-cost energy savings with recently installed Solar Panels. A $40K+ investment, the electricity bill is only $8 per month. Solar Panels balance paid off with full price offer. Please call me with any questions. Thanks for showing.
